# CppAD code-generated test artifacts. Tests now route codegen to the package
# build directory via getCodegenPath() (see */include/*/package_path.h.in), so
# the source tree must stay clean. The rule below guards against legacy
# pollution and any out-of-source CppAD usage that still falls back to
# getPath().
**/auto_generated/
